{
  "stem": "9471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how we-- we came to the first-- Gospic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember we came there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the same night, they took my husband, me and baby, and one other couple.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took us back to Koprivnica, because I had a baby and sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know why they took us back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't let us go to the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They let us stay again in this warehouse over the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us in train again and then brought us first in Gospic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not in the camp, they put us in prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And oh, God, when they put us in prison and closed the door, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were about-- my husband, me and baby, and my girlfriend with her daughter and her in-laws, we were in-- in one room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we heard crying and yelling, because other prisoners, they were beaten, terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were all night together and, you know, cling to each other, what's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in morning, they took us from this prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us to-- to camp where I told you about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I met my family there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were there already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's tragic, but it was the happiest moment for my life, when I saw my parents there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were so happy to see me, you know, and to see, first time, the grandchild.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't do anything there, nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just being there together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what did I want to say?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then after, other camp, when they separate us, you know, the men, they went to Jasenovac.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the worst camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I don't know, maybe 10 or 15 people survived from thousands of people in this.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
